8/07/24
What is Web Designing?
Presenting content / information online, for any business / organization in 
the form of a website.

What are the technologies used in Web Designing?
HTML + CSS + Java Script

HTML:-
HTML (HyperText Markup Language), is used to create the Basic Structure and content of a webpage

CSS:-
CSS (Cascading Style Sheets) is used for the design of a webpage – where everything is placed and how it 
looks.

Java Script:-
JavaScript is used to define the interactive of a webpage that help to engage users.

