10/07/24
Types of Web Site:-
Dynamic Website
Static Website

Static Website:-
 It only displays Information
 Quick to develop & easy to host
 Less number of pages
 No Frequent Modifications
 Rare updates & It is manually done only by designer
 Technologies used in Static Websites : HTML + CSS + JS

Dynamic Website:-
 Deals with Database & Logic
 Time consuming & requires developers with full scripting Skills
 Multiple number of pages
 Automatic updates
 Technologies used in Dynamic Websites : PHP, ASP, MySQL etc
Example: E-commerce websites, Job Portals etc

