Html basic
HTML Document
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h1>This is TCA Training & Development</h1>
<p> We provide Industrial & Corporate Training and works on different 
Industry Projects.<p>
</body>
</html>
Html Headings-
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h1>TCA Provides Training For</h1>
<h2>CSE/IT Branch</h2>
<h3>Civil Branch</h3>
<h4>Mechanical Branch</h4>
<h5>EC/EE Branch</h5>
<h6>Diploma Holders</h6>
</body>
</html>

Html Marquee tags-
<html>
<head>
<title>HTML Link</title>
<body>
<h1 style="text-align:center;">Marque</h1>
<h2 style="color:blue;"><marquee>This is Marquee</marquee></h2>
<h2 style="color:green;"><marquee width=50%>This Marquee is half of Screen</marquee></h2>
<h2 style="color:red;"><marquee direction="right">Marquee Right Side</marquee></h2>
<h2 style="color:purple;"><marquee direction="up">Marquee Up</marquee></h2>
<h2 style="color:lime;"><marquee direction="down">Marquee Down</marquee></h2>
</body>
</head>
</html>

