HTML Paragraphs

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h1>About TCA</h1>
<p>TCA Gurgaon is the best training institute in Gurgaon for project-
based industrial training, skill development & corporate trainings. 
TCA Gurgaon is one of the leading training institute in Gurgaon to 
learn cutting-age technology. We here at TCA provides best 
infrastructure to develop and deploy your projects during your 
industrial training in Gurgaon. </p>
</body>
</html>
HTML Paragraphs with Break Line<br>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h1>About TCA</h1>
<p>TCA Gurgaon is the best training institute in Gurgaon for project-
based industrial training, skill development & corporate 
trainings.<br> TCA Gurgaon is one of the leading training institute in 
Gurgaon to learn cutting-age technology. <br> We here at TCA 
provides best infrastructure to develop and deploy your projects during 
your industrial training in Gurgaon. </p>
</body>
</html>
HTML Links
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h1> This is Heading</h1>
<a href="hare.html">Hare File</a>
</body>
</html>

HTML Links another example
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<h1>How to create links in HTML</h1>
<p> Links moves you from one page to another page</p>
<a href = "https://www.tcagurgaon.in">TCA</a>
</body>
</html>

